class.name: BehaviorSettingAtt
class.abstract: Enables attribute access to BKT options.

method.abstract: Retrieves environment informations for the BKTAccessRights parameter.

method.name: GetBKTBehaviorOperationMessageInfo
method.abstract: Retrieves environment informations for the BKTBehaviorOperationMessage parameter.

method.name: GetBKTSpecificationTreeInfo
method.abstract: Retrieves environment informations for the BKTSpecificationTree parameter.

method.name: SetBKTAccessRightsLock
method.abstract: Locks or unlocks the BKTAccessRights parameter.

method.name: SetBKTBehaviorOperationMessageLock
method.abstract: Locks or unlocks the BKTBehaviorOperationMessage parameter.

method.name: SetBKTSpecificationTreeLock
method.abstract: Locks or unlocks the BKTSpecificationTree parameter.

method.name: BKTAccessRights
method.abstract: Returns or sets the BKTAccessRights parameter.

method.name: BKTBehaviorOperationMessage

method.name: BKTSpecificationTree
method.abstract: Returns or sets the BKTSpecificationTree parameter.
